[{"text": "I just came back from a community", "start": 15.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that holds the secret to human survival.", "start": 17.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's a place where women run the show,", "start": 21.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "have sex to say hello,", "start": 24.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and play rules the day --", "start": 26.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where fun is serious business.", "start": 28.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And no, this isn't Burning Man", "start": 31.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or San Francisco.", "start": 33.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 35.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Ladies and gentlemen, meet your cousins.", "start": 37.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is the world of wild bonobos", "start": 40.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the jungles of Congo.", "start": 43.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Bonobos are, together with chimpanzees,", "start": 45.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "your living closest relative.", "start": 48.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "That means we all share a common ancestor,", "start": 51.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "an evolutionary grandmother,", "start": 54.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who lived around six million years ago.", "start": 56.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now, chimpanzees are well-known", "start": 60.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for their aggression.", "start": 62.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 64.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But unfortunately,", "start": 67.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have made too much of an emphasis", "start": 69.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of this aspect", "start": 71.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in our narratives of human evolution.", "start": 73.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But bonobos show us", "start": 76.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the other side of the coin.", "start": 78.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "While chimpanzees", "start": 80.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are dominated by big, scary guys,", "start": 82.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "bonobo society", "start": 85.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is run by empowered females.", "start": 87.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "These guys have really worked something out,", "start": 91.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "since this leads to a highly tolerant society", "start": 94.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where fatal violence", "start": 97.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "has not been observed yet.", "start": 99.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But unfortunately,", "start": 102.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "bonobos are the least understood", "start": 104.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the great apes.", "start": 106.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They live in the depths of the Congolese jungle,", "start": 108.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it has been very difficult to study them.", "start": 111.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The Congo is a paradox --", "start": 114.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a land of extraordinary biodiversity and beauty,", "start": 117.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "but also the heart of darkness itself --", "start": 121.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the scene of a violent conflict", "start": 124.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that has raged for decades", "start": 127.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and claimed nearly as many lives", "start": 129.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as the First World War.", "start": 132.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Not surprisingly,", "start": 136.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this destruction also endangers bonobo survival.", "start": 138.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Bushmeat trades and forest loss", "start": 142.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "means we couldn't fill a small stadium", "start": 145.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with all the bonobos that are left in the world --", "start": 148.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we're not even sure of that to be honest.", "start": 150.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Yet, in this land of violence and chaos,", "start": 154.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "you can hear hidden laughter", "start": 158.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "swaying the trees.", "start": 161.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Who are these cousins?", "start": 163.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We know them as the \"make love, not war\" apes", "start": 166.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "since they have frequent, promiscuous", "start": 170.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and bisexual sex", "start": 172.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to manage conflict", "start": 174.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and solve social issues.", "start": 176.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Now, I'm not saying this is the solution", "start": 178.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to all of humanity's problems --", "start": 180.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "since there's more to bonobo life", "start": 184.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "than the Kama Sutra.", "start": 186.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Bonobos, like humans,", "start": 188.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "love to play throughout their entire lives.", "start": 190.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Play is not just child's games.", "start": 192.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "For us and them,", "start": 194.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "play is foundational for bonding relationships", "start": 196.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and fostering tolerance.", "start": 199.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's where we learn to trust", "start": 201.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and where we learn about the rules of the game.", "start": 203.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Play increases creativity", "start": 206.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and resilience,", "start": 208.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it's all about the generation of diversity --", "start": 211.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "diversity of interactions,", "start": 214.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "diversity of behaviors,", "start": 216.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "diversity of connections.", "start": 218.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And when you watch bonobo play,", "start": 221.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you're seeing the very evolutionary roots", "start": 223.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of human laughter, dance", "start": 226.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and ritual.", "start": 228.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Play is the glue", "start": 230.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that binds us together.", "start": 232.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Now, I don't know how you play,", "start": 234.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but I want to show you a couple of unique clips", "start": 237.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "fresh from the wild.", "start": 239.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "First, it's a ball game bonobo-style --", "start": 241.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I do not mean football.", "start": 244.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So here,", "start": 247.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have a young female and a male", "start": 249.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "engaged in a chase game.", "start": 251.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Have a look what she's doing.", "start": 254.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It might be the evolutionary origin of the phrase,", "start": 256.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"she's got him by the balls.\"", "start": 258.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 260.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Only I think that he's rather loving it here, right?", "start": 263.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Yeah.", "start": 267.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 269.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So sex play is common", "start": 271.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in both bonobos and humans.", "start": 273.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And this video is really interesting", "start": 275.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because it shows --", "start": 277.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this video's really interesting", "start": 279.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because it shows the inventiveness", "start": 281.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of bringing unusual elements into play --", "start": 283.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "such as testicles --", "start": 286.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and also how play both requires trust", "start": 289.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and fosters trust --", "start": 292.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "while at the same time being tremendous fun.", "start": 295.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But play's a shapeshifter.", "start": 297.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 299.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Play's a shapeshifter,", "start": 302.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and it can take many forms,", "start": 304.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "some of which are more quiet,", "start": 306.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "imaginative, curious --", "start": 308.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "maybe where wonder is discovered anew.", "start": 310.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I want you to see,", "start": 313.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this is Fuku, a young female,", "start": 315.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and she is quietly playing with water.", "start": 317.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I think, like her,", "start": 319.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we sometimes play alone,", "start": 321.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we explore the boundaries", "start": 323.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of our inner and our outer worlds.", "start": 325.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And it's that playful curiosity", "start": 328.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that drives us to explore, drives us to interact,", "start": 330.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and then the unexpected connections we form", "start": 334.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are the real hotbed for creativity.", "start": 337.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So these are just small tasters", "start": 341.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "into the insights that bonobo give us", "start": 344.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to our past and present.", "start": 346.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But they also hold a secret for our future,", "start": 349.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a future where we need to adapt", "start": 352.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to an increasingly challenging world", "start": 354.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "through greater creativity", "start": 357.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and greater cooperation.", "start": 359.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The secret is that play is the key", "start": 361.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to these capacities.", "start": 364.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In other words,", "start": 366.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "play is our adaptive wildcard.", "start": 368.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In order to adapt successfully", "start": 370.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to a changing world,", "start": 372.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we need to play.", "start": 374.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But will we make the most of our playfulness?", "start": 378.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Play is not frivolous.", "start": 381.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Play's essential.", "start": 383.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "For bonobos and humans alike,", "start": 385.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "life is not just red in tooth and claw.", "start": 388.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In times when it seems least appropriate to play,", "start": 391.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it might be the times when it is most urgent.", "start": 394.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And so, my fellow primates,", "start": 398.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "let us embrace this gift from evolution", "start": 401.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and play together,", "start": 404.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as we rediscover creativity,", "start": 406.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "fellowship and wonder.", "start": 409.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 411.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 413.26, "duration": 2.0}]